{"tid":2478452,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"巴西疫情嚴峻　首次單日錄得逾4千宗死亡病例","createTime":"2021-04-07T05:29:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T05:50:44.000Z","uid":241764,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8519d7080eaa7b13a7a769f691aecd7cea88f66c","tid":2478452,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T05:29:16.000Z","msg":"(節錄)<br />\n<br />\n巴西的新型肺炎疫情嚴峻，在變種病毒肆虐下，首次在24小時內錄得超過4千宗死亡病例，累計接近33萬7千人不治，僅次於美國。<br />\n<br />\n另外，巴西單日新增接近8萬7千宗確診，累計1310多萬宗。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1584535-20210407.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1584535-20210407.htm&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtEcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=7df27dd3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1584535-20210407.htm&h=cffb1dc6\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1584535-20210407.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08c40914f40f18cb8657ba90f52718d078501c51","tid":2478452,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T05:29:45.000Z","msg":"科興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d6fe8fba740f3df7f21c58778840ab1e5d2e3fe","tid":2478452,"uid":288968,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"08c40914f40f18cb8657ba90f52718d078501c51","tid":2478452,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T05:29:45.000Z","msg":"科興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T0